04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c87884fc3ad8f84b4651161f214db6840f0a17","tid":1526672,"uid":228934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:05:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">墊pad寧考緊immi海關懲教同icac</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[突發] 警察惡行 請retweet<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1523089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1523089</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n當年有份聯署既人，大部分都走哂，仲留得係度既人，你都估到佢係咩人？？<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有人性嘅，應該一早 劈炮，唔再做 cctvb吧！但係佢仲要做足7年，做到2019 年今日，然後佢想洗白拎光環，叫3毛 錢7開post造勢，想拎光環夾橫行直入海關警察入境. 繼續染紅政府為藍屍發聲。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n我心裡梗係想佢係因良心發現而辭職啦<br />\n佢係鬼良心發現辭職咩<br />\n係<em>比</em>班同事投訴佢番工唔做野掛住化妝<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">覺得比人杯先辭渣<br />\n仲帶哂光環咁<br />\n屋企警察世家攞咩光環<br />\n<br />\n最後 cctvb假新聞記者主播無一個無辜 <br />\n唔好亂信任何消息 為佢哋洗白<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警 主播 死 全 家</span></span>"},{"pid":"44a052adbee7aacb463dd1981ec5d3a5681d235e","tid":1526672,"uid":38373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:07:36.000Z","msg":"正路，狗鐵專載狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2512ddd38787d16ed9825145ee65f27a50b7683e","tid":1526672,"uid":63808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"559bca7bfceeb5da6c9dff2ad51d546ee27b6905","tid":1526672,"uid":293227,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:01:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵從來唔會停，只係轉黎載狗<br />\n<br />\n以後撞防火鐘，掉野落路軌